sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving (Raw Deployment)
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,CloudStorage: Flow 1 — InferenceService Model Serving (Raw Deployment)

        participant Client as External Client
        participant GW as HTTPRoute / VirtualService<br/>Gateway / Ingress
        participant AuthProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OpenShift Serving Cert
        participant Predictor as Inference Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant CloudStorage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>GW: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        GW->>AuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (OpenShift serving cert)
        Note right of AuthProxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>validates caller identity
        AuthProxy->>Predictor: HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>No auth (trusted)
        Predictor-->>AuthProxy: Prediction Response
        AuthProxy-->>GW: HTTPS Response
        GW-->>Client: HTTPS Response

        Note over Predictor,CloudStorage: Init Container Phase (before serving)
        participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>(Init Container)
        StorageInit->>CloudStorage: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Provider Credentials (IAM/SA/Token)
        CloudStorage-->>StorageInit: Model Artifacts
    end

    %% Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Request Routing
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client2,vLLM: Flow 2 — LLMInferenceService Request Routing

        participant Client2 as External Client
        participant GW2 as Gateway<br/>(HTTPRoute)
        participant EPP as EPP Scheduler<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
        participant vLLM as vLLM Workload Pod<br/>8000/TCP

        Client2->>GW2: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        GW2->>EPP: gRPC/9002<br/>Configurable encryption
        Note right of EPP: Endpoint Picker Protocol<br/>selects optimal backend
        EPP->>vLLM: HTTP/8000<br/>Configurable encryption
        vLLM-->>EPP: Inference Response
        EPP-->>GW2: gRPC Response
        GW2-->>Client2: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 3: InferenceGraph Routing
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client3,ISVCBackend: Flow 3 — InferenceGraph Routing

        participant Client3 as External Client
        participant Route as OpenShift Route /<br/>Knative Service
        participant IGRouter as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant ISVCBackend as InferenceService<br/>Backends

        Client3->>Route: HTTPS/443 (TLS Reencrypt)<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Route->>IGRouter: HTTP/8080<br/>TokenReview + SAR (if enabled)
        Note right of IGRouter: Graph traversal:<br/>sequence, splitter,<br/>ensemble, switch
        IGRouter->>ISVCBackend: HTTP/8080<br/>Istio mTLS (in mesh)
        ISVCBackend-->>IGRouter: Response
        IGRouter-->>Route: Aggregated Response
        Route-->>Client3: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 4: Local Model Caching
    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over LMCtrl,NodeStorage: Flow 4 — Local Model Caching

        participant LMCtrl as LocalModel Controller
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant LMNodeAgent as LocalModelNode Agent<br/>(DaemonSet)
        participant DownloadJob as Download Job<br/>(batch/v1)
        participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant NodeStorage as Node-Local Storage<br/>Filesystem

        LMCtrl->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Note right of LMCtrl: Creates PV/PVC<br/>for model storage
        LMNodeAgent->>K8sAPI: Creates download Job
        DownloadJob->>CloudStore: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Provider Credentials
        CloudStore-->>DownloadJob: Model Artifacts
        DownloadJob->>NodeStorage: Write to local disk<br/>SELinux/MCS (ODH)
        Note right of NodeStorage: Models cached<br/>on node for<br/>fast serving
    end
